{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "法尔吉德 第1话 为了大家使用力量",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "这里就是圣城啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "喔，这地方挺气派的啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗨，你们就是\\n法尔吉德和巴比吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我叫尤蒂尔，\\n请多关照。你们的事\\n我听格蕾丝说了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你们……挺不容易的吧。\\n被“结社”关起来，\\n吃了不少苦头……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "是啊……“结社”确实没给我们\\n留下什么好的回忆。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "认识的人一个接一个死去，\\n只有我活了下来……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔吉德……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "但是……正因如此，\\n我才不能逃避不前！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我要替那些死去的人\\n努力活下去才行！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n你真的很坚强。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "不，我觉得这家伙\\n只是神经大条而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哈哈，不管怎么说，\\n总比萎靡不振要好得多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这座城很安全。\\n希望你们能忘记“结社”的事，\\n在这里自由生活。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "好的！谢谢你，\\n尤蒂尔！\\n今后要受你关照了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嘿咻……呼。\\n洗的衣服有这么多，\\n也真够累的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "啊，是洗好的衣服吗？\\n我来帮你晾吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "哎呀，你是那位……\\n不，我自己来就行了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "听说你吃了不少苦头，\\n现在就好好休息吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "谢谢你这么体谅我……\\n可待着不动怪难受的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我还是想做一些\\n力所能及的事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "来，我们开始晾吧！\\n哇！量好多啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "呵呵，你真是个怪人……\\n嘴上说着好多，\\n还满脸笑容地晾衣服。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "因为这不是挺好的吗。\\n有一种……活着的感觉。或者说，\\n让人觉得今天也是太平的一天。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "太平……的确如此呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "能像这样放心地晾衣服，\\n就是太平的证明。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "好了，衣服也晾完了，\\n接下来我还能帮什么忙……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "嗯？等一下，\\n怎么那么吵？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01",
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "兰扎卜，在西边的森林！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好，交给我吧！\\n看我收拾掉那群魔兽！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "有魔兽出现了？\\n我们也参战吧，巴比！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "诶？不用了吧？\\n交给他们就……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "但是这里的人们救了我们，\\n我们要知恩图报才行！\\n巴比，我们走！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "喂，就算你一个人去也……\\n啊……已经走掉了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "真是的，听我说完啊。\\n不过算了，一直受人恩惠\\n我面子也挂不住。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "发现魔兽了！在那里！\\n兰扎卜，我们上！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶？这声音是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我也来支援！\\n尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂喂，别乱来啊，\\n你没接受过战斗训练吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "没问题的！我有这股力量……\\n看招……诶？巴比？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "哇、哇啊啊啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "危险！都说了让你退后！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "我就说吧，你一个人\\n又没法战斗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "啊，巴比！你也太慢了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "是你冲得太快了。\\n这下你知道\\n我有多珍贵了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "是是，我懂啦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "你哪里懂了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "都说我懂了啦，总之先上阵！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "“龙锁装填”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔吉德！？那副模样……\\n难道是“结社”的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "对。这见鬼的力量是“结社”\\n那群家伙给我们的……\\n叫“龙锁装填”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "但是，有了这股力量，\\n就能保护他人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "所以我决定了，\\n要为大家使用这份力量！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔吉德……\\n好，那就助我一臂之力吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "嗯！来吧我们上，巴比！\\n哈啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好……都收拾掉了，\\n多亏有法尔吉德帮忙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "是啊，本来我还觉得你是\\n“结社”的受害者，得由我们\\n保护才行……看来没这个必要。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "虽然战斗方式还很稚嫩……\\n可你很有骨气，我欣赏你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊！今后也助我们\\n一臂之力吧！法尔吉德！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "当然！\\n我会全力以赴的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "呼……今天也……\\n很努力了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "喂，法尔吉德！？\\n要睡起码到床上去啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "呼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "没救了……\\n纹丝不动啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "真是的……你努力过头啦。\\n帮忙做家务、帮助有困难的人，\\n还去消灭魔兽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "搞不懂……为了别人努力\\n到这份上，能有什么好处啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}